            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "God I miss when Total War games were good.. The latest Warhammer slop and the DLC scandals have me really apprehensive about Medieval III, but I am still holding out hope that CA will remember what made these games good in the first place: Better balance, historical elements, no bloat. Just basic skill trees, basic agents, and raw destruction.\n"
        },
