            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Still my favorite total war game of all. \nI have tried and played many but I always come back to this one. Of course there are countless things that could be improved, but the overall experience is still peak to me for a historical total war game. A man can dream about Shogun 3 after Medieval 3.\n\n"
